<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="MTA67">
<l>peyaruṅ karuṅkaṭalē nōkkumā ṟoṇpū</l>
<l>vuyaruṅ katiravaṉē nōkku – muyirun</l>
<l>tarumaṉaiyē nōkkumoṇ ṭāmaraiyāḷ kēḷva</l>
<l>ṉoruvaṉaiyē nōkku muṇarvu</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>The river looks towards the moving black sea. The bright flower</l>
<l>looks towards the One with rays who rises. All living beings</l>
<l>look towards the one who has Dharma.  The intellect looks towards the One,</l>
<l>the husband of her on the bright lotus.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
